              <div class="ligne-avis__corps">
                <div class="ligne-avis__haut"><b>Thomas Legrand</b><span class="etoiles"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2l3 6.6 7 .8-5.2 4.8L18.3 21 12 17.4 5.7 21l1.5-6.8L2 9.4l7-.8z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2l3 6.6 7 .8-5.2 4.8L18.3 21 12 17.4 5.7 21l1.5-6.8L2 9.4l7-.8z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2l3 6.6 7 .8-5.2 4.8L18.3 21 12 17.4 5.7 21l1.5-6.8L2 9.4l7-.8z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2l3 6.6 7 .8-5.2 4.8L18.3 21 12 17.4 5.7 21l1.5-6.8L2 9.4l7-.8z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2l3 6.6 7 .8-5.2 4.8L18.3 21 12 17.4 5.7 21l1.5-6.8L2 9.4l7-.8z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg></span><span class="ligne-avis__quand">Il y a 2 jours</span></div>
                <p>Intervention rapide et efficace. Très professionnel, je recommande !</p>
              </div>
